postPerformanceRecords.t.sol
├── when the caller is not the owner
│   └── it should revert
└── when the caller is the owner
    ├── when the reporting epoch is lte the last updated epoch
    │   └── it should revert
    └── when the reporting epoch is gt the last updated epoch
        ├── when input arrays don't match in length
        │   └── it should revert
        └── when input arrays match in length
            ├── when the sum of performances is 0
            │   └── it should revert
            └── when the sum of performances is not 0
